short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: New Tab with Divers Theme Background

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Change the background image on new tabs to feature cool Divers and Divers related images! The extension also provides users with a Custom Web Search on the New Tab.

By installing "Divers Tab" extension, you agree to the EULA and Privacy Policy, and to set your new tab page to Divers Background.
